   Brad, 58, donned a stylish chocolate brown knee-length skirt with a long matching cardigan for the event. The skirt came down to the actor’s knees, showing off his toned calves, while Brad’s chunky black combat boots came up past his ankles. Brad teamed the ensemble with a salmon pink button-up shirt, which fit loosely and was left partly open to reveal a large god necklace. The actor completed his look with a pair of tortoise shell shades and wore his blond hair in a relaxed, tousled do.  